text: The Tesla Model 3 is a electric mid-size car with a fastback body style built and made by Tesla. It was launched on 2017. The car became more cheaper for people who cannot buy older Tesla vehicles. It was approved New York City Taxi car. == Sales == In February 2019, Tesla Model 3 became the best-selling luxury car in United States. == References == == Other websites == * Category:2020s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles Category:Tesla automobiles Category:Electric vehicles
